theStory:
Fitzybrypto, real name likely Fitzy, runs a verified X account with 8,435 followers, branding himself with a humorous bio: 'PhD in retard communication helping the lower IQ understand how things work. Posts are not financial advice.' Active in the Solana meme coin ecosystem, his content blends degen humor, simple crypto explanations, and token promotions. Early activity in June-July 2025 shows casual engagement, like replying in threads with quips (e.g., June 4, 2025: 'What do women love?' in a meme context, https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/1930364250070909024) and openly 'pumping bags' on July 25, 2025 ('Im busy pumping my bags', https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/1948866955965804781), indicating a trader mindset without specific projects highlighted.

By late 2025 and into January 2026, Fitzy evolved into a community leader, particularly with $BOOB, a boob-themed meme coin. On January 19, 2026, he addressed rumors of a Community Takeover (CTO), calling buyers 'retarded pigs' for front-running but proceeded to CTO after the original team allegedly exploited Keep A Breast charity ('Ok fuck it ctoing $boob', https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/2014377042528153876). He ramped up boob memes, like January 26's 'We must protect boob at all costs' (https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/2015755631609721292), driving engagement. The charity endorsed him positively on January 23 ('@Fitzybrypto is the guy', https://x.com/keepabreast/status/2014648937190228342), boosting legitimacy.

His reputation is mixed: praised as transparent and capable by supporters for leading multi-million mcap CTOs previously, but criticized for potential pump/dumps. On January 23, amid charity bullishness ('Breast cancer charity bullish...', https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/2014789214060138924), @Pokepal007 accused him of fresh wallets and pump/dump risks. No major rugs or exits noted; he critiques others like James Wynn on January 11 (https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/2010170602074849785). Overall, he's a niche degen voice, evolving from casual shiller to CTO leader.

promotionHistory.details: Took over from malicious original team; praised by Keep A Breast; multiple boob memes and calls to hold (e.g., https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/2015135813160288583)
Thread replies like 'Imagine the easiest play' (https://x.com/Fitzybrypto/status/1948866606320250942); prior multi-mcap CTOs mentioned by others

publicPerception.supporters: Degen community aping due to CTO track record ('GOAT @Fitzybrypto', https://x.com/stekisteks/status/2014570244732551472); Keep A Breast charity for delivery and coordination ('@Fitzybrypto is the guy', https://x.com/keepabreast/status/2014648937190228342).
publicPerception.critics: Accusers like @Pokepal007 claiming fresh wallets and pump/dump on $BOOB ('Are they all your fresh wallets?', https://x.com/Pokepal007/status/2014804173372751891); minor FUD from ignored shills.

controversies.summary: Accused by @Pokepal007 of pump/dump scheme using fresh wallets on $BOOB, questioning hold intentions amid charity tie-in.
controversies.resolution: Unresolved; Fitzy continued posting bullish content without direct response.
